#: ../../../admin-guide/media/fimc.rst:124
msgid "5. Device mapping to video and subdev device nodes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/media/fimc.rst:126
msgid ""
"There are associated two video device nodes with each device instance in "
"hardware - video capture and mem-to-mem and additionally a subdev node for "
"more precise FIMC capture subsystem control. In addition a separate v4l2 sub-"
"device node is created per each MIPI-CSIS device."
